Name: Suspect Enemy
About the game: Description Our planet is on the brink of destruction, and in order to survive, we need to colonize another planet... You are 1 in volunteers to colonize another planet but be careful! There is a killer among you who must be found and kicked before the whole crewmate is killed. Crewmate To win, you need to complete all tasks or kicked all killers in the vote. Urgently repair sabotage, if you do not have time then you will lose. Keep track of other crewmate using cameras or the admin panel. Monitor the condition of the crewmate with a medical sensor. Report any corpses found or suspicious activity of other players. Vote to banish the killer. Killer Kill crewmate members and frame other players by giving false information or accusing them of murder. Pretend to complete tasks so as not to arouse suspicion. Use teleports carefully to quickly change your location. Use sabotage to make it easier to kill or force the crewmate to move around the map. Close doors to hide or stop a crewmate. Features In-game voice and text chat. Color randomization. Full game customization: More killers, more tasks and so much more.
